    <item>
      <title>Rotate images</title>
      <link>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-06-rotate-images/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 16:42:00 -0600</pubDate>
      <guid>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-06-rotate-images/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Given an image stored in a 2D Python array, we provide code for rotation by different degrees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;clockwise-by-90-degrees&#34;&gt;Clockwise by 90 degrees&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transpose then reverse each row&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;rotate&lt;/span&gt;(image):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; len(image)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(n):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; j &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(i&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, n):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            image[i][j], image[j][i] &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; image[j][i], image[i][j]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(n):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        row &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; image[i]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        l, r &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, n&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; l &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; r:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            row[l], row[r] &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; row[r], row[l]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; image
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;counterclockwise-by-90-degrees&#34;&gt;Counterclockwise by 90 degrees&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reverse each row then transpose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transpose is 180 degrees&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;rotate_counterclockwise&lt;/span&gt;(image):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; len(image)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(n):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        row &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; image[i]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        l, r &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, n&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; l &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; r:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            row[l], row[r] &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; row[r], row[l]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            l &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            r &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(n):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; j &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(i&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, n):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            image[i][j], image[j][i] &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; image[j][i], image[i][j]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; image
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Max profit with bid and ask</title>
      <link>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-05-max-profit/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 16:41:00 -0600</pubDate>
      <guid>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-05-max-profit/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We edit the popular problem series of &lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/problems/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock/&#34;&gt;best time to buy and sell stocks&lt;/a&gt; to allow differing buy and sell prices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;max_profit&lt;/span&gt;(buy, sell):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    n &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; len(buy)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    dp_holding, dp_not_holding &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    dp_holding &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;sell[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, n):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        tmp &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; dp_holding
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        dp_holding &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; max(dp_holding, dp_not_holding &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; buy[i])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        dp_not_holding &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; max(tmp &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; sell[i], dp_not_holding)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; dp_not_holding
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Remove duplicate from unsorted array</title>
      <link>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-04-remove-duplicates/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 16:40:00 -0600</pubDate>
      <guid>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-04-remove-duplicates/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We provide an implementation of removing duplicated values from an (unsorted) array.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sorted version (&lt;a href=&#34;ttps://leetcode.com/problems/remove-duplicatesfrom-sorted-array/description/&#34;&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;remove_duplicate&lt;/span&gt;(arr):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    seen &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; []
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; num &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; arr:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        seen&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(num)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; seen
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(remove_duplicate([&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;]))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(remove_duplicate([&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;]))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(remove_duplicate([&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;[1, 2, 4]
[5, 4, 1]
[5, 2, 1]
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Time and space: $O(N)$. Not possible to be $O(1)$ since we do not know where the duplicate is located and no ordering information. Extra space is needed to check if value has been encountered before.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>O(1) methods for test statistics</title>
      <link>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-03-o-of-1-statistics-copy/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 16:38:00 -0600</pubDate>
      <guid>https://honglizhaobob.github.io/math-problems/problems/2026-03-08-03-o-of-1-statistics-copy/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In this note, we provide code to compute useful statistics in a dataset in $O(1)$ space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;sliding-window-max-and-min&#34;&gt;Sliding window max and min&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; collections &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; deque
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;sliding_window_maximum&lt;/span&gt;(nums, k):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;        nums: observed data stream
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;        k:    window size ( k &amp;lt;= len(nums) )
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;    &amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    res &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [] 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    q &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; deque()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(k):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        num &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; nums[i]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; q &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; nums[q[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]] &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; num:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            q&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;pop()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        q&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(i)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    res&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(nums[q[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;]])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(k, len(nums)):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        num &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; nums[i]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# adjust window&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; q &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; q[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; i&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;k:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            q&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;popleft()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; q &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; nums[q[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]] &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; num:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            q&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;pop()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        q&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(i)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        res&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(nums[q[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;]])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; res
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# test&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;nums &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;k &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# =&amp;gt; [1, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(sliding_window_maximum(nums, k))
